text: Rungis is a commune. It is in the Val-de-Marne department in France. In 2019, 5,657 people lived there. The commune is in the southern suburbs of Paris, from the center. It is best known as the home of the large wholesale food market Marché d'Intérêt National de Rungis. Category:Communes in Val-de-Marne
title: Rungis
